            <h4 class="text-yellow-400 font-bold mb-2">High Conflict Rates</h4>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-400 space-y-1">
              <li>• Reduce sync interval to catch changes faster</li>
              <li>• Use CRDT types for frequently modified fields</li>
              <li>• Review data model for concurrent write hotspots</li>
              <li>• Consider implementing field-level locking in UI</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-950/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-white/5">
            <h4 class="text-yellow-400 font-bold mb-2">Local Storage Errors</h4>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-400 space-y-1">
              <li>• Check available disk space</li>
              <li>• Verify write permissions for storage path</li>
              <li>• Reset local storage with <code class="text-yellow-300">full_resync()</code></li>
              <li>• Enable encryption only after storage initialization</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-950/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-white/5">
            <h4 class="text-yellow-400 font-bold mb-2">Data Not Syncing</h4>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-400 space-y-1">
              <li>• Verify sync filter isn't too restrictive</li>
              <li>• Check that collections are in sync list</li>
              <li>• Ensure version vectors are incrementing</li>
              <li>• Verify server has sync endpoint enabled</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

